<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WebView Embed</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .wv-outer {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 720px;
      height: 520px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      border: 1.5px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .wv-topbar {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .wv-body {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      display: flex;
    }
    .wv-scroll-rect {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 1.5px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: scroll;
      background: #fff;
      cursor: grab;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }
    .wv-scroll-rect:active { cursor: grabbing; }
    .wv-bottombar {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .nav-btn {
      background: none;
      border: 0.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .nav-btn:hover { background: #f3f4f6; }
    .url-bar {
      flex: 1;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border: 0.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .inner-content { width: 860px; padding: 20px; }
    .page-header {
      background: #0f3460;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .page-header h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 4px; }
    .page-header p  { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin: 0; }
    .stats-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .stat-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-box .num { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: #111; }
    .stat-box .lbl { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 3px; }
    .banner {
      background: #EAF3DE;
      border: 1px solid #C0DD97;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .banner i  { font-size: 22px; color: #3B6D11; }
    .banner h3 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #27500A; margin: 0 0 2px; }
    .banner p  { font-size: 12px; color: #3B6D11; margin: 0; }
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      border: 0.5px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .card-thumb {
      height: 90px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .card-body { padding: 10px; }
    .card-tag   { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: #A32D2D; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .card-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: #111; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .card-meta  { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .article h2 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: #111; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .article p  { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.7; color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .status-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #27c93f; flex-shrink: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="wv-outer">

    <!-- TOP BAR -->
    <div class="wv-topbar">
      <div class="dot" style="background:#ff5f56;"></div>
      <div class="dot" style="background:#ffbd2e;"></div>
      <div class="dot" style="background:#27c93f;"></div>
      <button class="nav-btn"><i class="ti ti-arrow-left" style="font-size:14px;"></i></button>
      <button class="nav-btn"><i class="ti ti-arrow-right" style="font-size:14px;"></i></button>
      <div class="url-bar">https://www.indiatoday.in</div>
      <button class="nav-btn"><i class="ti ti-refresh" style="font-size:14px;"></i></button>
    </div>

    <!-- BODY -->
    <div class="wv-body">
      <div class="wv-scroll-rect" id="wv-sr">
        <div class="inner-content">

          <div class="page-header">
            <h1>India Today — Breaking News</h1>
            <p>Latest stories across politics, tech, sports, and more</p>
          </div>

          <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat-box"><div class="num">1.2M</div><div class="lbl">Daily readers</div></div>
            <div class="stat-box"><div class="num">340+</div><div class="lbl">Stories today</div></div>
            <div class="stat-box"><div class="num">48</div><div class="lbl">Correspondents</div></div>
            <div class="stat-box"><div class="num">7</div><div class="lbl">Regional langs</div></div>
            <div class="stat-box"><div class="num">24/7</div><div class="lbl">Live coverage</div></div>
          </div>

          <div class="banner">
            <i class="ti ti-radio"></i>
            <div>
              <h3>Live: Parliament winter session — Day 4</h3>
              <p>Follow all updates from Lok Sabha and Rajya Sabha in real time</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#EEEDFE;">🏛️</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Politics</div><div class="card-title">Budget session key bills tabled in Lok Sabha</div><div class="card-meta">2 hrs ago · Delhi</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#E1F5EE;">🤖</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Technology</div><div class="card-title">India's AI policy framework draft released</div><div class="card-meta">4 hrs ago · Mumbai</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#E6F1FB;">🏏</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Sports</div><div class="card-title">India vs Australia 3rd test match preview</div><div class="card-meta">1 hr ago · Sports desk</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#EAF3DE;">🌱</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Environment</div><div class="card-title">COP31 commitments: where India stands</div><div class="card-meta">5 hrs ago</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#FAEEDA;">🎬</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Entertainment</div><div class="card-title">Bollywood box office — weekend recap</div><div class="card-meta">3 hrs ago</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-thumb" style="background:#FAECE7;">🏥</div>
              <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tag">Health</div><div class="card-title">AIIMS Delhi launches AI diagnostic pilot</div><div class="card-meta">6 hrs ago</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="article">
            <h2>In depth: India's economic outlook for 2026</h2>
            <p>Economists across major institutions have flagged a mix of optimism and caution for India's GDP trajectory heading into the next fiscal year. With manufacturing sector output rising 6.2% year-on-year and services maintaining robust performance, the base case scenario remains positive.</p>
            <p>However, global headwinds including elevated oil prices, sluggish export demand from key partners, and domestic inflation pressures present notable downside risks. The RBI's monetary policy committee faces a delicate balancing act as it approaches its next review cycle.</p>
            <p>Infrastructure spending under the National Infrastructure Pipeline continues to act as a demand multiplier, particularly in tier-2 and tier-3 cities where construction activity has accelerated sharply over the past 18 months.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BOTTOM BAR -->
    <div class="wv-bottombar">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
        <div class="status-dot"></div>
        <span style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">Secure connection</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
        <span style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;">
          <i class="ti ti-arrows-move" style="font-size:13px;"></i> Drag to scroll
        </span>
        <span style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">860px wide content</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script>
    (function () {
      var el = document.getElementById('wv-sr');
      var drag = false, sx, sy, sl, st;
      el.addEventListener('mousedown', function (e) {
        drag = true; sx = e.pageX; sy = e.pageY;
        sl = el.scrollLeft; st = el.scrollTop;
        el.style.cursor = 'grabbing';
      });
      document.addEventListener('mouseup', function () {
        drag = false; el.style.cursor = 'grab';
      });
      document.addEventListener('mousemove', function (e) {
        if (!drag) return;
        e.preventDefault();
        el.scrollLeft = sl - (e.pageX - sx);
        el.scrollTop  = st - (e.pageY - sy);
      });
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
